&lt;p&gt;At Marqeta, we&#39;re on a mission to revolutionize the way money moves. As pioneers in the field of embedded finance, we&#39;re tapping into a market opportunity that&#39;s worth trillions. Our card issuing platform offers unparalleled flexibility and control, enabling companies to issue cards, authorize transactions, and manage payment operations in real time. We power some of the most renowned brands in the new economy, including Block, Cash App, Affirm, Instacart, Doordash, Uber, and Walmart. Today, nearly 8 out of 10 Americans use a product powered by Marqeta every week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Marqeta’s &lt;strong&gt;Director, GTM Operation&lt;/strong&gt;s you will be responsible for establishing and executing a strong operational cadence, bringing structure and sustainable, scalable processes to support business growth and ensure cross-functional alignment. In this role, you will be responsible for managing the sales incentive compensation design and executing the sales compensation program; overseeing the selection, implementation and ongoing maintenance of tools and technologies to support GTM and revenue operations; managing opex and headcount budgeting &amp;amp; tracking processes, and driving operational rigor and excellence across the GTM organization. As a change agent for the organization, you will rely on data-driven insights and rigorous process assessment to drive operational efficiency within the GTM org.&lt;/p&gt;
