&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;NOTE: if you are based within 35 miles of our Oakland, California, New York City (Midtown) or London office, you will be expected to be in-office 2 days / week. The Talent team will share more details if selected for the Recruiter Interview.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
