&lt;p&gt;As Marqeta’s GTM Strategy &amp;amp; Operations Manager based in the UK, you will help build and execute the strategy and operations for a best-in-class sales organisation. In this role, you will partner with Sales to use insights to develop internal sales processes and operational activities to maximise sales productivity. You will cover core areas including reporting on sales performance and trends, working cross-functionally on initiatives to increase sales efficiency, and driving strategic planning.&lt;/p&gt;
