&lt;li&gt;Lead and mentor a high-performing engineering team, improving velocity and system reliability through intelligent workflows and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the technical and business-facing leader in customer and regulatory escalations, translating complex compliance scenarios into scalable platform improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
