&lt;li&gt;The Identity platform is architected to be extensible — enabling Marqeta to expand into new markets with different regulatory frameworks (e.g., new jurisdictions, AML regimes, or licensing requirements) without requiring a platform rebuild.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customers and regulators view Marqeta as trusted, expert partners in identity and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
