&lt;p&gt;As Marqeta&#39;s &lt;strong&gt;Senior Director, Investor Relations&lt;/strong&gt;, you will lead and evolve the company&#39;s IR program during a pivotal period of growth and strategic transformation. Reporting directly to the SVP, Head of IR, you will serve as the primary architect of Marqeta&#39;s investment narrative and a trusted partner to executive leadership, the Board of Directors, and the global investment community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a finance athlete — equally comfortable modeling the income statement, building earnings messaging, engaging with analysts and shareholders, and advising the C-suite on how the market is pricing Marqeta’s story. You bring intellectual horsepower, executive presence, and a deep command of what moves investor sentiment in the high-growth fintech and payments space. You translate Marqeta’s complex, multi-faceted platform business into a compelling and credible financial narrative — and you make every touchpoint with the Street count.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While we work &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.marqeta.com/blog/2022/05/10/flexible-first&quot;&gt;Flexible First&lt;/a&gt;, this role requires&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; in-person presence at our Oakland office once a week&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;. We’d love for you to join us!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Impact You’ll Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Earnings &amp;amp; Disclosure: &lt;/strong&gt;Lead preparation of all quarterly earnings materials — press releases, earnings supplements, CFO/CEO scripts, and Q&amp;amp;A — with the rigor of an operator and the polish of a communicator.&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Investor Engagement: &lt;/strong&gt;Serve as the company’s primary spokesperson with institutional investors and sell-side analysts. Own the investor conference strategy and calendar and investor day planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equity Story &amp;amp; Messaging: &lt;/strong&gt;Partner with the CFO and CEO to develop and continuously refine Marqeta’s long-term investment thesis, messaging frameworks, and forward-looking financial narratives.&lt;/li&gt;
